│ trip count from the 'MainMiddle' predecessor and zero from the iteration      │
│ count check predecessor. In the provided reproducer, the loop structure and   │
│ analysis lead to a situation where such a PHI is not found, triggering the    │
│ assertion.\n\n2. Analyzing opt's Log:\nThe opt run shows an immediate         │
